data.description: Welcome to this stunning mid-century modern gem! This 5-bedroom, 2-bath home is a masterpiece of design and functionality. As you enter, you will be greeted by a custom tile entryway and sleek design, setting the tone for the elegance that awaits. The dining area boasts colorful pendant glass lighting that beautifully complements the rich hardwood floors, creating an inviting atmosphere. Curl up by the cozy wood-burning fireplaces that grace both the dining and living rooms. The kitchen offers solid wood cabinetry, modern hardware, and a butcher block island. The striking blue glass tile backsplash adds a pop of color and style. Stainless steel appliances and double ovens complete this culinary haven. Retreat to the family room. Enjoy the red oak hardwood flooring and natural light that streams through the picture windows. The main floor includes the primary bedroom,  a spacious laundry/utility room, an additional bedroom, and a stylish bathroom complete with double vanities. The mid-century pendant lighting and custom, backlit stairwell will captivate you as you descend  to discover an expansive family room with a third fireplace, that opens to a covered patio with a new self-cleaning hot tub and an expansive fenced backyard, perfect for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. Three additional bedrooms downstairs feature custom wood blinds, unique lighting fixtures and customizable closet inserts. Home offers plenty of storage, under stairs, a large unfinished space and a cold storage room, perfect for your canned goods. A brand new bathroom downstairs adds a modern touch. This home is nestled on almost a half acre, complete with fruit trees, a 4-zone programmable drip system and plenty of room to play or garden.  The front has been tastefully landscaped to bring out the best of this mid-century home.  Complete with a two car garage, ample parking and a large RV pad.  Plus two storage sheds and a cord of madrone firewood.
